name: Sheik
description:
Will likely do a v2. It's pretty good now but has issues with her outfit.

If your are prompting her in clothes remove the '1girl' tag if you want to stay on model. If not then you do you haha.

Can you take off her mask:
If you put scarf and mask in the negatives then yep.

And her head wrap:
Ummmm.... no? I think?

As Usual:
Trained on Anything v3
Demos are on Anything v4.5 with LoRA weight 1
